      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{% comment %}\n  Reciclibros — Bloc de routage page Contacto (v2)\n{% endcomment %}\n\n<div class=\"rl-contact-router\" id=\"rl-contact-router\">\n  <div class=\"rl-cr-inner\">\n    <h2 class=\"rl-cr-title\">¿En qué podemos ayudarte?</h2>\n    <p class=\"rl-cr-intro\">Selecciona la opción que mejor se adapte a tu consulta:</p>\n\n    <aside class=\"rl-cr-faq\">\n      <div class=\"rl-cr-faq-text\">\n        <strong>Si tienes una duda</strong>, te recomendamos consultar primero nuestras preguntas frecuentes. Es posible que encuentres la respuesta de forma inmediata.\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"rl-cr-faq-btn\" href=\"/pages/preguntas-frecuentes\">Ver preguntas frecuentes</a>\n    </aside>\n\n    <div class=\"rl-cr-grid\">\n\n      <a class=\"rl-cr-card\" href=\"https://shopify.com/101993316686/account\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-tag\">Pedidos</span>\n        <h3 class=\"rl-cr-card-title\">Pedidos realizados en Reciclibros</h3>\n        <p class=\"rl-cr-card-text\">Accede a tu Área de Cliente y haz clic en <strong>«Informar de un problema»</strong> en el pedido correspondiente.</p>\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-card-cta\">Ir a mi Área de Cliente <span class=\"rl-cr-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&rarr;</span></span>\n      </a>\n\n      <a class=\"rl-cr-card\" href=\"mailto:compra@reciclibros.com\">\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-tag\">App</span>\n        <h3 class=\"rl-cr-card-title\">Ventas a través de la app Reciclibros</h3>\n        <p class=\"rl-cr-card-text\">Para cualquier consulta sobre una venta realizada desde la app, escríbenos directamente por correo.</p>\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-card-cta\">Escribir a compra@reciclibros.com <span class=\"rl-cr-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&rarr;</span></span>\n      </a>\n\n      <a class=\"rl-cr-card\" href=\"/pages/donar-o-vender#formulario\">\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-tag\">Donación</span>\n        <h3 class=\"rl-cr-card-title\">Donación de libros y recogida</h3>\n        <p class=\"rl-cr-card-text\">¿Quieres donar tus libros o solicitar una recogida? Completa el formulario de donación.</p>\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-card-cta\">Ir al formulario de donación <span class=\"rl-cr-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&rarr;</span></span>\n      </a>\n\n      <a class=\"rl-cr-card\" href=\"#ContactForm\" data-rl-scroll-to-form>\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-tag\">Otras dudas</span>\n        <h3 class=\"rl-cr-card-title\">Dudas generales</h3>\n        <p class=\"rl-cr-card-text\">Si tu consulta no encaja en ninguna de las opciones anteriores, utiliza el formulario que encontrarás a continuación.</p>\n        <span class=\"rl-cr-card-cta\">Ir al formulario de contacto <span class=\"rl-cr-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&rarr;</span></span>\n      </a>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .rl-contact-router {\n    font-family: 'Work Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #333333;\n    padding: 0 20px 8px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-inner {\n    max-width: 960px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-title {\n    font-family: 'Francois One', 'Work Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 36px);\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    margin: 0 0 8px;\n    color: #333333;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-intro {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    color: #4f4f4f;\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-faq {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 14px;\n    background: #e8f1eb;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    padding: 24px;\n    margin: 0 0 24px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-faq-text {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n    color: #006837;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-faq-btn {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #006837;\n    color: #ffffff !important;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    padding: 12px 28px;\n    transition: opacity .2s ease;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-faq-btn:hover { opacity: .85; }\n\n  .rl-cr-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 749px) {\n    .rl-cr-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 8px;\n    background: #ffffff;\n    border: 1px solid #dedede;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    padding: 24px;\n    text-decoration: none !important;\n    color: #333333 !important;\n    transition: border-color .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, transform .2s ease;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card:hover,\n  .rl-cr-card:focus-visible {\n    border-color: #ff6400;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(51, 51, 51, .08);\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card:focus-visible {\n    outline: 2px solid #ff6400;\n    outline-offset: 2px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-tag {\n    align-self: flex-start;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: .04em;\n    color: #ff6400;\n    background: #fff5f0;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    padding: 4px 14px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card-title {\n    font-family: 'Francois One', 'Work Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin: 4px 0 0;\n    color: #333333;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card-text {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n    color: #4f4f4f;\n    margin: 0;\n    flex-grow: 1;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card-cta {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #ff6400;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-arrow {\n    display: inline-block;\n    transition: transform .2s ease;\n  }\n  .rl-cr-card:hover .rl-cr-arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }\n</style>\n\n<script>\n  (function () {\n    var trigger = document.querySelector('[data-rl-scroll-to-form]');\n    if (!trigger) return;\n    trigger.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n      var form = document.querySelector('form[action^=\"/contact\"]');\n      if (form) {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        form.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });\n        var firstField = form.querySelector('input, textarea');\n        if (firstField) setTimeout(function () { firstField.focus({ preventScroll: true }); }, 500);\n      }\n    });\n  })();\n</script>",
